'''Shiogama Shrine''' (しおがまじんじゃ) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in central [[:en:Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama Prefecture]][[:en:Wakayama (city)|Wakayama City]]{{ill|Wakaura|ja|和歌浦|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakaura|qq=}}. It is also written as 鹽竈神社.
